meta {
  name: Get Deposit Methods
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

get {
  url: {{BASE_URL}}/private/v1/deposits/methods?limit=
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

params:query {
  limit: 
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{AUTH_TOKEN}}
}

settings {
  encodeUrl: true
}

docs {
  # Deposit
  
  ## 1. Get All Payment Methods
  
  ![image.png](attachment:62ca9803-1553-4c0e-a2d9-d3acbcd384de:image.png)
  
  ## 2. Get Payment Form By Payment Method ID
  
  ![image.png](attachment:8c1387b4-b783-42f9-8e06-dfa8a6420e4b:image.png)
  
  ## 3. Check Has Pending Payment Order(Only for fireblocks)
  
  ![image.png](attachment:8f99b891-71c6-4072-844a-243f8a7da9d6:image.png)
  
  **if pending payment order returns not null , show wallet_address.address for user until order is expired or user cancelled the order.**
  
  ## 4. Get Currencies
  
  ![image.png](attachment:c138bc19-41bd-493b-b201-9bbc944e29e1:image.png)
  
  ## 5. Get Exchange Rate
  
  ![image.png](attachment:50b25931-5cd0-4f57-8368-c192e4f59f93:image.png)
  
  ## 6. Get Fireblocks Deposit Wallet Address(Create Pending Payment Order)
  
  ![image.png](attachment:17760fe9-ea29-4c3f-957c-a21136da1bd1:image.png)
  
  ```jsx
  {
      "method_id": "de00632j",     // payment method id
      "payment_currency": "Ethereum Test (Sepolia)",  // payment currency
      "trading_currency": "USD",      // deposit currency
      "trading_platform": "fortex",   // deposit platform (List of value:[mt4,mt5,mtr,wta,ctrader,fortex])
      "trading_connection_id": "z80wqyxy", // deposit connection id
      "trading_id": "STEV1", //deposit trading account 
      "trading_amount": "2.96",  // deposit amount 
      "payment_total": "0.001", // payment amount
      "payment_fee": "0",  //payment fee
      "request_type": "deposit",  // request type (deposit)
      "convert_way": "P2T", // input Payment Amount to calculate Deposit Amount (for backend check rate)
      "form_data": { 
          "qtvwvfzu": [],  // deposit method's form data field
          "form_id": "ob543bux"   //deposit method's form id
      }
  }
  
  1. when you deposit to wallet , there is no need to pass trading_platform,trading_connection_id and trading_id
  2. when you use fireblcoks to deposit, convert_way must be P2T. And you need to calculate trading_amount by payment_total with exchange rate.
  ```
}

