                "information": {
                    "en-us": "1",
                    "zh-cn": "<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.44; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Bonus trigger conditions\n&nbsp; &nbsp; </p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.57; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1. Client Deposit Bonus&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: inherit; font-family: Avenir, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;, Roboto, -apple-system, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.57;\">\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; · The bonus can be given to the depositing client himself, or to the superior client of the depositing client, and the bonus level can be customized.\n&nbsp; &nbsp; </p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.57;\">\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; · Bonus to trading account credit, balance, and bonus to wallet.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: inherit; font-family: Avenir, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;, Roboto, -apple-system, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.57;\">\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; · Support bonuses based on the percentage of each deposit amount or a fixed amount, and different bonus ratios can be set for different deposit intervals.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: inherit; font-family: Avenir, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;, Roboto, -apple-system, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.57;\">\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; · Bonuses are supported based on a percentage of the total deposit amount or a fixed amount during the event, and different bonus ratios can be set for different deposit intervals.\n&nbsp; &nbsp; </p>"
