            {
                "id": "yxhhwpyw",
                "platform": "other",
                "label": {
                    "en-us": "线下汇款-English",
                    "zh-cn": "线下汇款"
                },
                "information": {
                    "en-us": "<h2 id=\"h2-u5883u5916u6C47u6B3E2\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(55, 61, 65); position: relative; line-height: 20px; z-index: -1; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">境外汇款</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">您需先准备加盖公章的合同或者协议，再通过银行网银或柜台向阿里云境外汇款收款账户进行汇款，具体汇款材料以当地银行要求为准。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意：境外汇款涉及资金跨境，且不支持专属账号方式，需要财务人工进行结汇及款项认领可能需要消耗较长时间。如不得不需要以此方式进行充值，请提前操作，以免余额不足造成欠费停机。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以下为阿里云境外汇款账户信息：</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">公司名称：Alibaba Cloud Computing Ltd.</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">汇款账号：571905493610901</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">开户银行（中文）：招商银行股份有限公司杭州武林支行</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">开户银行（英文）：Hangzhou Wulin Branch of CMB</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">银行代码（Swift Code）：CMBCCNBS281</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">12 码的 CNAPS 系统行号：308331012054</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">收款银行地址（英文）: International Science and Technology Building, Block A in Hangzhou West Lake District Road No. 391</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">公司的英文地址： No. 969，Wenyi Road ,Yuhang District, Hangzhou, Zhejiang Province，China</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">完成银行汇款后，再<a href=\"https://ia.aliyun.com/home?channel=ticket&amp;mark=ticket-submit\" title=\"提交工单\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; background: 0px 0px; color: rgb(255, 106, 0); outline: none;\">提交工单</a>，提供汇款凭证及加盖公章的合同或协议，申请财务进行人工结汇和款项认领。</p>",
                    "zh-cn": "<h2 id=\"h2-u5883u5916u6C47u6B3E2\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(55, 61, 65); position: relative; line-height: 20px; z-index: -1; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">境外汇款</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">您需先准备加盖公章的合同或者协议，再通过银行网银或柜台向阿里云境外汇款收款账户进行汇款，具体汇款材料以当地银行要求为准。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意：境外汇款涉及资金跨境，且不支持专属账号方式，需要财务人工进行结汇及款项认领可能需要消耗较长时间。如不得不需要以此方式进行充值，请提前操作，以免余额不足造成欠费停机。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以下为阿里云境外汇款账户信息：</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">公司名称：Alibaba Cloud Computing Ltd.</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">汇款账号：571905493610901</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">开户银行（中文）：招商银行股份有限公司杭州武林支行</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">开户银行（英文）：Hangzhou Wulin Branch of CMB</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">银行代码（Swift Code）：CMBCCNBS281</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">12 码的 CNAPS 系统行号：308331012054</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">收款银行地址（英文）: International Science and Technology Building, Block A in Hangzhou West Lake District Road No. 391</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">公司的英文地址： No. 969，Wenyi Road ,Yuhang District, Hangzhou, Zhejiang Province，China</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">完成银行汇款后，再<a href=\"https://ia.aliyun.com/home?channel=ticket&amp;mark=ticket-submit\" title=\"提交工单\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; background: 0px 0px; color: rgb(255, 106, 0); outline: none;\">提交工单</a>，提供汇款凭证及加盖公章的合同或协议，申请财务进行人工结汇和款项认领。</p>"
                },
